description: From the creator of the 2005 hit graphic novel Black Hole comes this new softcover edition of his other masterpiece of modern horror. Big Baby is a particularly impressionable young boy named Tony Delmonte, who lives in a seemingly typical American suburb until he sneaks out of his room one night and becomes entangled in a horrific plot involving summer camp murders and backyard burials. Burns' clinical precision as an artist adds a sinister chill to his droll sense of humor, and his affection for 20th-century pulp fiction permeates throughout, creating a brilliant narrative that perfectly captures the unease and fear of adolescence.
On the day before Christmas Nick Fury, Agent of S.H.I.E.L.D. must infiltrate a HYDRA base to celebrate the holidays . . . head bashing style.
name: Ol' Saint Nick

description: Sam's never shaken the memory of the beautiful and deadly 'Emma of the Isles.' When a mysterious box arrives containing a plane ticket to Scotland, a cellphone and a gun, Sam doesn't waste any time catching the first flight out. But in a rural village, where's Emma? Why are the locals a little...off? Can Sam handle this mission without his brother?
name: Caledonia, Emma of the Isles pt 1 of 4

description: The Thing is expecting to celebrate the holidays at a Chinese buffet when a familiar villain threatens ruin. The big orange bundle of cheer sets out to save Christmas before the egg rolls are gone.
name: Chinese Food for Christmas

description:
Batman and Robin #16: Batman and Robin Must Die - Part Four: Black Mass

Robin is seconds away from pledging his soul forever to Dr Hurt in order to open the ancestor box and complete the resurrection of the Bat God Barbatos... but there comes a strange whistling... Gotcha! Someone got there first! 
 
Batman: The Return of Bruce Wayne - Part Six: The All Over

From the very edge of time to the dawn of man, Bruce Wayne has struggled through space, time and memory rebuilding the myth of Batman, saving the world in perpetuity... But is this the big all-over? 
 
Batman 700: Time and the Batman - And Tomorrow

The last section of DC's fantastic 700th anniversary issue lets us peer into Gotham's dystopian futures to see what lies ahead for the Batman of tomorrow... and tomorrow... and tomorrow!
name: Batman and Robin #16/Batman: The Return of Bruce Wayne #6/Batman #700

description:
'3:10 To Thanagar'!

Take a trip into outer space with Batman's latest adventure, 3:10 To Thanagar! Of course, the Dark Knight isn't alone in this issue's brand new comic strip - this time he teams up with the super hero of the skies, the savage HAWKMAN!

Batman's Alien Heroes

Batman has loads of great super hero friends on Earth that he can count on when he's in trouble, but he's not alone when he's in outer space either! Check out the greatest moments from the best of Batman's alien friends and heroes!

Also inside this issue:

  • Feature: When Aliens Attack! - Part Two
  • Episode guide: 'Dawn Of The Dead Man'
  • Fun feature: Super Hero Name Generator
  • Batman's Secret Files: Despero
  • Win Batcave sets from Imaginext!
  • Pull-out poster
  • Brain-bending puzzles and activities
  • Bat-Signals: Your letters and artwork
name: '3:10 To Thanagar'!

volume.name: Batman: The Brave and the Bold

description:
'3:10 To Thanagar' Part Two!

Hawkman has teamed up with Batman to capture Byth, a shapeshifting criminal from the planet Thanagar! Find out how they fare in their mission in this latest comic strip adventure in Batman: The Brave And The Bold!

The Joker's Chaotic Christmas

Everybody loves Christmas, no one more so than the Joker! He likes to dish out his own brand of chaos during the holiday season. Check out what this fiendish foe has in store for this festive time of year, as we present the Joker's alternative Christmas!

Also inside this issue:

  • Batman's Hero File: Hawkman
  • Feature: What if Blue Beetle fought Aquaman?
  • Pull-out poster
  • Brain-bending puzzles and activities
  • Bat-Signals: Your letters and artwork
name: '3:10 To Thanagar' Part Two!

volume.name: Batman: The Brave and the Bold

description: How would medieval mankind defend itself from an all-out alien invasion in the 13th century? Answer: With great difficulty! Witness the beginning of the end of mankind in the pages of Alivs Rex!
name: TPB

description: “The Lazarus Tree,” Part Three—Veteran artist Mike Vosburg joins the creative team for this link in the Lazarus Tree mystery, which finds Moriarty reflecting on a case in 1880's Kingston, Jamaica. Answers are revealed to present-day questions, including the identity of the sniper that has been murdering residents of Kyauktada and stoking the fires of rebellion.
name: The Lazarus Tree, Part Three

description: CHAOS is over. The future holds many mysteries, but the past can never be forgotten. As Ironhide looks back at what was, he comes to realize that it may hold the key to what lies ahead. A new peace has settled, and a new time has come for the Autobots, for the Decepticons... for Cybertron.
name: Pax Cybertronia

description:
"THE GATHERING STORM," Part Two

No longer willing to sit idly by as outside forces manipulate his life, Jim sends a violent warning in order to secure an uneasy alliance with one of his greatest enemies. Meanwhile, an old friend is pulled deeper into the pit of intrigue surrounding the new Hellspawn, as Marc's search into Jim's mysterious past takes a surprising turn.
name: The Gathering Storm, Part 2 (of 6)

description: Dark Horse is tempted to call Little Lulu the "comeback comic" of the year, but truth be told, Lulu's been a treasured part of the entertainment canon for years! Dark Horse Books is proudly presenting the complete library of classic Marge's Little Lulu comics in a reader-friendly series of affordable paperback volumes. A rascally but good-hearted seven year old with an endless supply of sass, oodles of smarts, and a wild imagination, Lulu is truly one of a kind.
name: Lulu Takes a Trip

volume.name: Little Lulu: Lulu Takes A Trip

description: THE IRREDEEMABLE/INCORRUPTIBLE CROSSOVER EVENT BEGINS! This month in the pages of IRREDEEMABLE or INCORRUPTIBLE…witness a life-changing tale from when the Plutonian was the world’s most beloved superhero and Max Damage was one of the most savage super-villains anywhere! Don’t miss the origin of this famous set of super-enemies in this 4-issue crossover event! This is the crossover event fans have been begging for! A can’t-miss issue of Mark Waid’s multiple Eisner and Harvey Award-nominated superhero series! NOT READING INCORRUPTIBLE TOO? You’re missing out! THE FIRST ISSUE OF THE IRREDEEMABLE/INCORRUPTIBLE CROSSOVER!
name: Redemption, Part One

description: SEE WHY CRITICS AND FANS LOVE ELRIC’S RETURN TO COMICS! The mystery is deepening for the Eternal Champion, as Elric, Hawkmoon, Corum and Eric Beck come face to face with nearly unstoppable forces of Law and Chaos. But can they find the key to restoring the balance in time to stop catastrophe across the Multiverse? New York Times bestseller Chris Roberson (SUPERMAN, iZOMBIE, STAN LEE’S STARBORN) and legendary fantasy author Michael Moorcock are bringing Elric back to comics in a big way in this sixth issue of the critically acclaimed series!

Cesar Ruiz is a hardened enforcer for a powerful drug cartel, and his young daughter isn't just along for the ride. Angela is a little girl growing to be a young woman in the long shadow of her criminal father, Cesar. What will a child do to win the respect of the most brutal enforcer in the Cali cartel? And how many people will Angela have to kill to get what she wants most?

On a rain soaked night in the heart of Bogota, a young girl witnesses a brutal murder by the hand of her father. This was no accident as her father wanted her to see. Snow Angel tells the story of Angela, a little girl growing up in the long shadow of her criminal father, Cesar. What would a child do to win the respect of the most brutal enforcer in the Cali cartel?
name: OGN

volume.name: Marge's Little Lulu and Tubby Annual

description: Art book of Zen Intergalactic Ninja.

volume.name: The Art of Zen Intergalactic Ninja

description: One man’s quest to become one like the gods through the book of death, finds himself being consumed by the powers that are within its pages as it controls his every thought and his actions. The search for mysterious murders continues. Kaaria (Dreadlocks) comes closer to the one known as Anakis. The one called Anakis lures Dreadlocks to a parallel dimension where the battle of the past and future collide as one.
name: GN

description: One mans quest to become one like the gods finds himself being consumed by the powers that are within its pages as it controls his every thought. The search for the mysterious murders continues as Kaaria (Dreadlocks) comes closer to the one that is behind it all. Dreadlocks comes face to face with the beast.
name: Part 1

description: Dreadlocks is lured into another dimension, Once he is there the search comes to an end, but the battle just begins. Pharohn teleports Nefatari and Elijah to the same dimension as Dreadlocks, I search of where Dreadlocks may be held. During their search fro Dreadlocks, Elijah and Nefatari encounters several obstacles only to get close to what their searching for.
name: Part 2

description: The closer Nefatari gets to Dreadlocks he becomes weaker while in the clutches of Set Tyophon. In this thrilling conclusion Set Typhons quest comes to an end but not without someone going down with him.
name: Part 3

description: The Dreadlock's origins.
name: Origins

description: Anthology Flip-Book.
name: None
Face to Face with the Madness
This Revolution Will Not Be Televison

description: In this new series of Dreadlocks, he is summoned by the Gods of Alkebulan. Dreadlocks has been given another mission by the Gods to stop the one called Serpentess “the Serpent witch”as she Search for ways to bring her father Apep back to life to destroy Dreadlocks and the Gods he serves. If Serpentess is victorious The Universe will no longer exist the way we know it to.”
name: Chapter 1

description: In the second installment the Unholy Disciples ship has landed. They are ready to take on Dreadlocks, only to find that Dreadlocks isn’t the only obstacle. The villain Serpentess has something in store for the Unholy Disciples.
name: Chapter 2

description: In the conclusion to The War of the Gods, BlackWatch and the Unholy disciples battle the evil Bloodstone who has just been freed by Serpentess and Vodum. This battle escalates until Dreadlocks is freed from the clutches of the dead souls of Bloodstone.
name: Chapter 3

description: Martin Mystère is summoned in front of a disquieting character, Colonel Bozzo, leader of a secret brotherhood whose goals aren’t exactly crystal-clear. The Colonel is asking him for help. Reluctantly, the Detective of the Impossible listens to an intricated story made of plots, strange artifacts and ancient secrets that he completely ignored; and he’s unwittingly involved in an occult war, fought away from the eyes of the world. A war whose target is chaos itself, and whose main warrior bears an ancient and feared name… This year Almanacco also features everything about the “mysterious” books, movies, TV series, and videogames of the year, as well as files about Fantomàs, De Torquemada and the horrors of Inquisition, and the monsters behind the corner “seen” by Dino Buzzati.
name: Almanacco del Mistero 2012

description: The introduction to BLACKWATCH, Pharohn is addressed by the God Tehuti about assimilating a group to continue the balance of the Nexus Galaxy and Universe 13 which is several Galaxies away from Earth. After Pharohn meditates and comes to his subconscious, He contemplates each individual for this new super group. The gathering will consist of Queen Nubia, Sheba, Mizraiim, Ragamuff and Third Eye. This group will be called “BLACKWATCH”.
name: Chapter 1

description: After the Battle of Bloodstone Dreadlocks stands among the gods as the soul of Bloodstone becomes imprisoned forever. As he parts way from the gods Dreadlocks deepest fears surface. The deceased ones, that materialize only in the darkness of night, posses the body of the one he cares about most. Once there is contact with the Deceased Ones spirits Dreadlocks will never be the same.
name: Chapter 1

description: Johnny Lucas goes off to fight in the desert storm war in 1992 for a cause that he thought was just. He’s trained as a Special Forces marine who learns the art of killing. Johnny Lucas begins to battle those that have taken his country hostage through the act of terror. After conflicting views from his superiors he takes a different route only to find himself imprisoned and freed 10 years later. Once freed from the life of the military he starts a new life living as a civilian that is short lived when he finds himself lost and back in the battle against the Secret Council in the year 2166 that started it all.
name: GN

description: This is a young woman who has been bestowed with the ability to enter Hell and return home at her will. She uses this unique ability to unlock the deeper mysteries that exist in her world. Who were her parents and why has she been entrusted with the gateway to Hell? Is Hell simply a place for the condemned to suffer, or is it more? Who is the mysterious angle Metatron?
name: Distant Pages
